latestIgtvVideos.title: @norafatehi recreated look of #pachtaoge 💫
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
So finally on popular demand, my first *MAKEUP TUTORIAL* is here🤩✔.
This tutorial is for the people who couldn't buy all makeup products  due to any reason. This tutorial has been made using minimum and essential makeup products in which you can look party ready in just 5 minutes✔.

Products used:-
💚@patanjaliproducts soundarya aloe vera gel for moisturizing and toning the skin.
💚Red @lakmeindia lisptick used as colour correcter to cancel out the look of skin discoloration.
💚@lakmeindia Perfecting liquid foundation to create an eventone of skin and to cover the flaws.
💚@hudabeauty beauty blender for blending the base and giving even tones after every makeup product addition.
💚Primer+concealer for oil-free long lasting base cover.
💚@lakmeindia Brown lipstick used as contouring stick to highlight the cheekbones and slimmer the nose.
💚@maccosmeticsindia Compact as baking the base to set the foundation and concealer.
💚@maccosmetics @hellokitty @urbandecaycosmetics brushes used throughout the makeup to adjust the base.

P.S :- You can add eyeliner, kajal, blusher, highlighter, eyelashes, mascara or any other additional makeup product to give your makeup enhanced and highlighted look, I didn't used much because I wanted a natural #nomakeupmakeuplook for the recreation.

Do like and promote this video if you find this helpful. ♥️

latestIgtvVideos.title: HAPPY GANESHA CHATURTHI💫🛕
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
It's a throwback to December,2016 when my sister @yamini.yadhuvanshi_official and I danced on this beautiful song 'Deva shree ganesha' by the movie 'Agneepath'. I find no other better chance to repost this throwback and to remember it than today, when Ganesha Chaturthi is being celebrated all over the India. And guess what? By lord ganesha's grace and blessings, we have crossed #115k views on this dance cover posted on your YouTube channel. I feel so connected to Lord Ganesha♥️💫🛕🙏May this ganesha chaturthi brings you a lot of happiness and joy. Wish you all a very happy ganesha chaturthi🛕💫♥️🙏
Oo my friend Ganesha, tu rehenaa saath hamesha🙏
